ActCanadian Net-Zero Emissions Accountability Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on which Section 23 of the Canadian Net-Zero Emissions Accountability Act Comes into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which section 23 of the CANADIAN NET-ZERO EMISSIONS ACCOUNTABILITY ACT COMES INTO FORCE in order to require the Minister of Finance to prepare and publish an annual report on the key measures that the federal public administration has taken to manage its financial risks and opportunities related to climate change.
